snippet: The election in GEORGIA takes place to day. A Governor, eight Members of Congress, and both branches of the State Legislature are to be chosen. The issue made is a new one. Old political divisions have very little to de with the contest....
lead_paragraph: The election in GEORGIA takes place to day. A Governor, eight Members of Congress, and both branches of the State Legislature are to be chosen. The issue made is a new one. Old political divisions have very little to de with the contest.
